FeatureDetails is a Form
    Layout
        display as text
            header2 of "<Feature>"
            paragraph
                visible when (InTrialPeriod)
                    visible when (AllowedToEnable)
                        button of "<EnableDisable>"
                            action is Enable
                            is primary
                    visible when (AllowedToDisable)
                        button of "<EnableDisable>"
                            action is Disable
            single column
                Description
                    use text area of 10 lines
            paragraph
                FeatureAvailability
                AvailableTo
